                          <p class="Para">Academic Analytics facilitate creation of actionable intelligence to enhance learning and student success. Visual Analytics methods like Motion Charts show changes through time by presenting animations within two-dimensional space and by changing element appearances. We present enhanced user interface features of the Visual Analytics tool EDAIME primarily designed for exploratory analysis of Academic Analytics. The tool supports various visualization methods and implements Motion Charts adjusted to academic settings. We also describe rich user interface abilities in detail.</p>
